<h2 class="api_method_name" data-subtopic="Courses" name="method.courses.update">
<a href="#method.courses.update" name="method.courses.update">
      Update a course
    </a>
<span class="defined-in"><a href="https://github.com/instructure/canvas-lms/blob/master/app/controllers/courses_controller.rb">CoursesController#update</a></span>
</h2>
<h3 class="endpoint">
    PUT /api/v1/courses/:id
  </h3>
<p>Update an existing course.</p>
<p>Arguments are the same as Courses#create, with a few exceptions
(enroll_me).</p>
<p>If a user has content management rights, but not full course editing
rights, the only attribute editable through this endpoint will be
âsyllabus_bodyâ</p>
